description:
Breath in Action: The Art of Breath in Vocal and Holistic Practice
Jessica Kingsley Publishers | 2009 | ISBN: 1843109425 | 256 pages | PDF | 1,6 MB

"Breath in Action" confirms the importance of breath as central to all vocal communication. Bringing together experts on voice and breath from a variety of backgrounds, the book provides a wealth of information on the art of breath and vocal communication.
